view.initial

Class InitialWindowImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.WindowAbstract
      • view.initial.InitialWindowImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InitialWindow, Window

    public final class InitialWindowImpl
extends WindowAbstract
implements InitialWindow
    An implementation of InitialWindow. It is composed by a InitialLevelList, a InitialOptions and a InitialSaveLoad object which have specific responsibilities.
